<T1>investigators have found evidence suggesting sandy hook shooter adam lanza was obsessed with previous mass murderers.</T1>

<T1.1>law enforcement sources told cbs news that lanza may have been motivated by a desire to outdo anders behring breivik.</T1.1>
<T1.1.1>breivik killed 77 people in norway in july 2011 through a bombing and a shooting spree on utoya island.</T1.1.1>
