<T1.2.2>vance stated that unsubstantiated details of the case are both hurtful and often inaccurate.</T1.2.2>
<T1.2.3>authorities have been largely tight-lipped about the investigation and will not release information until it is finished.</T1.2.3>

<T1.3>investigators are conducting a comprehensive review of evidence related to the shooting.</T1.3>
<T1.3.1>hundreds of law enforcement personnel are analyzing ammunition, examining the gunman's medical history and computer use, and talking to witnesses.</T1.3.1>
<T1.3.2>a source confirmed investigators found evidence that lanza "was obsessed" with other mass murderers.</T1.3.2>
<T1.3.3>a final report on the newtown shooting is expected in the summer.</T1.3.3>
